      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the S54-powered legend. Featuring a high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, the powertrain delivers razor-sharp throttle response up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis maintains its original structural rigidity, featuring a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation or fluid seepage. Every bushing, damper, and seal remains in peak operational condition, ensuring the telepathic handling characteristics that define the marque. A true collector-grade specimen with comprehensive service documentation and zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
